This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of Computational Linguistics (cs.CL) as it deals with the concept of phonemes in speech science and technology. It may also belong to the sub-category of Sound (cs.SD) as it discusses the sounds of speech. Additionally, it could be categorized under Machine Learning (cs.LG) as the paper investigates the use/misuse of a term in the research community. It may also be relevant to Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Social and Information Networks (cs.SI) as it discusses the implications of a psychological phenomenon in the research community.
